Resort Income Investors 1996 loss narrows . Resort Income Investors Inc , which is in liquidation , said Monday it had a loss of $ 8 . 3 million or $ 1 . 99 a share for the year ended December 31 , compared to a loss of $ 26 . 6 million or $ 6 . 41 a share a year ago . The decreased loss resulted from a reduction in the number of assets in liquidation , the company said . As of December 31 , the company ' s four remaining investment loans had a carrying value of $ 4 . 2 million , after $ 7 . 0 million for allowances for impairment of three of the company ' s loans , the company said . ( ( Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
